a blood transfusion.

293
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,840
But our supply is running low.

294
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:15,680
Could the family step forward
for a blood test?

295
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,120
I'll do it.

296
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,160
Siyan.

297
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,680
It's okay. I'll be right back.

298
00:18:35,279 --> 00:18:35,960
Does it hurt?

299
00:18:38,039 --> 00:18:38,599
I'm fine.

300
00:18:39,279 --> 00:18:41,000
